📁 Project Structure

```
📂 project/
│
├── Dataset/                        # Raw YAML stock data (by date)
├── symbol_csvs/                   # Cleaned individual stock CSVs (1 per symbol)
├── stock_summary.csv              # Summary of key metrics for all stocks
├── all_returns.csv                # Daily & cumulative return per stock
├── monthly_returns.csv            # Monthly gainers/losers
├── correlation_matrix.csv         # Correlation heatmap matrix
├── stock_data.db                  # SQLite database
│
├── app.py                         # Streamlit app code
├── PowerBI_Dashboard.pbix         # Power BI interactive visuals
├── Nifty50_Project_Presentation.pptx
├── Nifty50_Final_Project_Report.pdf
└── README.md                      # This file
